      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、すみません\nわざわざお時間を取ってもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm sorry for\ntaking your time like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい気にしないでくれ\nそれで、相談があるって聞いたけど、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't worry about it.\nSo‚ you mentioned you have something to discuss. What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私も……\nユニットを組ませてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I…\nCould I have a special team too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりだな。私「も」ってことは……\n雫と天動さんのユニットを見てそう思ったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's quite sudden. The \"too\" implies…\nDid you get the idea after seeing Shizuku and Tendo's team?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも、雫ちゃんと瑠依ちゃんのライブを見て\nいいなと思ったから、というよりは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ but it's not just that.\nAfter seeing Shizuku-chan and Rui-chan's live performance‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "結果としてのライブより、そこに至るまで二人が\n悩んでぶつかって、成長したことに刺激を受けたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized it's not about the end result of the live but the\njourney of two people struggling and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん月ストの活動を\n中途半端にするつもりはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "growing together that inspired me.\nOf course‚ I have no intention of doing things half-heartedly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "どんどん一体感が出て\n練習もライブも楽しくなってますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for Moon Tempest. As we become more cohesive‚\nboth practice and live performances become more enjoyable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、これからグループとしてもっと\n成長していくには……個人の成長も必要なのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I believe that for our group to grow even more‚\nindividual growth is essential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
